873
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:43,440
so I'd think,

874
00:38:44,599 --> 00:38:45,239
"Forget it.

875
00:38:46,559 --> 00:38:47,400
Next time."

876
00:38:52,519 --> 00:38:53,920
