What's wrong?

900
00:40:53,960 --> 00:40:54,320
Nothing.

901
00:40:55,577 --> 00:40:56,711
Did you catch a cold?

902
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:57,400
No.

903
00:40:58,320 --> 00:40:59,229
What's wrong?

904
