It's nothing.

906
00:41:03,199 --> 00:41:06,679
I'm just sensitive to this scent.

907
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:10,480
You scared me.

908
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:11,599
I thought you caught a cold

909
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:13,000
