912
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:26,199
Did you forget to take your meds?

913
00:41:27,039 --> 00:41:27,559
Meds?

914
00:41:28,622 --> 00:41:29,960
I've put them in the container.

915
00:41:30,559 --> 00:41:32,639
I was too busy picking you up,
